WEBVTT

NOTE Fictional Hartwell-Mercer demonstration. No real family data appears.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.613
Family trees preserve conclusions. Kin
Resolve preserves

00:00:03.613 --> 00:00:06.710
questions, records, uncertainty, and next
steps.

00:00:06.710 --> 00:00:10.000
This tour uses only fictional
Hartwell–Mercer data.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.959
Bring in a plain GEDCOM as a named,
durable source. The original

00:00:13.959 --> 00:00:17.918
export is staged privately, processing
state survives a refresh,

00:00:17.918 --> 00:00:22.000
and nothing enters the archive merely
because a file was selected.

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:26.264
Incoming additions, edits, conflicts, and
deletions become an explicit

00:00:26.264 --> 00:00:30.223
review. Safe changes can be approved
together; ambiguity requires

00:00:30.223 --> 00:00:34.000
a decision; remote deletion keeps the
local record by default.

00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:37.234
Research stays organized around a
question, not just

00:00:37.234 --> 00:00:40.531
a person. Evidence can strengthen or
weaken competing

00:00:40.531 --> 00:00:43.766
hypotheses, confidence remains visible,
and the case

00:00:43.766 --> 00:00:47.000
keeps the next search tied to the reason
it matters.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:50.474
Source transcripts remain close to the
people and cases they

00:00:50.474 --> 00:00:54.179
inform. Cohort one deliberately excludes
binary source media, so

00:00:54.179 --> 00:00:58.000
the hosted boundary stays narrow,
understandable, and enforceable.

00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:01.508
Quality and privacy checks run
deterministically inside Kin

00:01:01.508 --> 00:01:05.373
Resolve. They prioritize date conflicts,
source gaps, and sharing

00:01:05.373 --> 00:01:09.000
risks without sending the archive to an
external AI provider.

00:01:09.000 --> 00:01:13.023
The developer preview uses scoped,
expiring, archive-bound

00:01:13.023 --> 00:01:16.838
tokens. A secret is shown once, only its
prefix remains

00:01:16.838 --> 00:01:21.000
visible, and revocation denies the next
request immediately.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:25.565
The exit path stays visible: download a
GEDCOM, keep the review trail,

00:01:25.565 --> 00:01:30.000
and request verified deletion. Apply
without sending family records.

